title: My Pet Pal
subtitle: iOS Application to keep track of your puppy's activities and well-being
description: React Native mobile app that enables users to collaboratively manage dog's daily activities. Worked on database design, backend APIs, front-end design, frontend and backend connection, error handling, and styling.
takeAway: Take Away: Building a polished iOS app with React Native / Improving user experience by implementing Keyboard Aware Scroll View / Handling numerous asynchronous actions
technology: Technology: React Native, Redux, Expo, Node.js, Knex,  Ajax, PostgreSQL

title: My Pet Pal
subtitle: iOS Application to keep track of your puppy's activities and well-being
description: MyPetPal is your solution to staying on top of your dog's daily activities. Stay updated on what your dog is up to, whether they are sleeping, walking, pottying, eating, etc. You can invite others to work together with you to ensure that your dog or dogs are well taken care of.
